page.html:
Thx Ranmi sama for 1year supporter

Hi there, you can call me Mitsuba
About me
English
I lived in Beijing few years ago and currently living in Vancouver Canada and can speak Chinese, English and i may start to learn Japanese. I started osu in May 2014 which is the first rhythm game i ever played and i mainly do 4keys but also would like to try 7&8keys to challenge myself sometimes. also played Malody on ipad for a while before i broke my touchscreen lol. My life goal is to become the best non stepmania 4k player which looks completely impossible :/

I always go on AFK for a while because it helps me with breaking skill barriers so that's why everytime you find me just had a break i may be start good at new patterns instead.(e.g from jumpstream player to all-rounder after an AFK)

I'm pretty close to a All-rounder while i have relative high jacking and speed skill and relatively higher jumpstream skill and lower controlling skill with decent ACC for my skill level
But i'm really bad at LNs and idk why tbh,Vibro because i cant vibrate my fingers and i can even go faster with my jacking position.
And i'm really bad at any overmapped or maps which doesnt follow the rhythms because my timing depends on my hearing system and without them i could barely keep my accuracy.
Also i HATE dump.files from Stepmania which a lot of Stepmania-OSU players loves. Although i won't be hostile to people who loves dumps but suggesting me dump files and talking about dumps to me may result in triggering me badly.

(just a note that in this case maps which contains dumpstream but followed the rhythm and not heavily overnoted will Not be concerned as a Dump file for me)




Hope you are fine after seeing all these shit i just written here xD ....

一般我到了瓶颈的时会afk x'd。
